title: r/Entitledparents I DESERVE TO LIVE IN YOUR HOUSE!
description:
r/Entitledparents In today's episode, OP lives in an apartment by the beach. Her landlord brings by a prospective tenant (the entitled father) to check out the apartment, and he actually has the audacity to say that he wants to sleep there for the night. When OP refuses, he comes the next day and demands to be let in so he and his family can live there for a few days. Is this guy nuts?!
